SUMMARY:Media Law and Press Freedom in the Current Administration (Webinar)
DESCRIPTION:Webinar: Media Law for Journalists: Media Law and Press Freedom in the Current Administration \nDate/Time: Tuesday\, March 31 at 6pm ET \nSummary: Journalists\, news organizations\, and other media companies are facing unprecedented challenges from multiple directions under the current administration. In this session\, we’ll evaluate the angles of attack and discuss how to exercise First Amendment rights in the face of hostility and near-constant threats.  \nSpeaker(s):\n \n\nJeffrey P. Hermes\, Deputy Director\, Media Law Resource Center\nGeorge Freeman\, Executive Director\, Media Law Resource Center \n\nRegister here: https://nahj.memberclicks.net/medialawpressfreedom
