 al\;">Brooklyn Public Library Williamsburg • 240 Division Ave.\, at Marcy A
 ve\, New York\, NY 11211 US</span><br><br>Zohran Mamdani’s election as mayo
 r proved that New Yorkers can work together and win against impossible odds
 .<span style="font-weight: normal\;"> He successfully campaigned on a messa
 ge of an affordable city that workers in New York deserve. To realize that 
 vision\, we’ve got to keep organizing not just with our neighbors but also 
 in our workplaces.</span><br><br><a href="https://workerorganizing.org/trai
 ning/nyc/#form"><u>We can win together. Sign up today.</u></a></h4><h4><br>
 <p><span style="font-weight: normal\;">EWOC will help you build the skills 
 and give you the resources you and your co-workers need to demand what you 
 deserve.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: normal\;">RSVP for our “Uni
 te &amp\; Win at Work” training below. Food service workers\, warehouse wor
 kers\, office workers\, public-sector workers\, and anyone with a job is we
